<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[اللَّهْوَجة]</span>: لَهْوَج عليه الخبرَ: إِذا خلطه.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">ولهوج اللحمَ:</span> إِذا لم يُنضجه.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
