<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c4">[التَّلَهْوُج]</span>: يقال: تَلَهْوَجْتُ اللحمَ:<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">مثل لَهْوَجْته:</span> إِذا لم تُنْضِجْه.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
